"title": "1418: miracles, responses to",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "1418",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Miracles often depend upon faith on the part of those who will benefit from them. Human responses to miracles take various forms. Some respond in faith and obedience, whilst others are confirmed in their unbelief and rebellion.</p>\n<h2>Faith and obedience required in the working of miracles</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs17:13-1Kgs17:15\">1KI 17:13–17:15</a></strong> <em>The widow gave Elijah her last meal before she could be miraculously provided for.</em> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod14:16\">EXO 14:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod14:21\">EXO 14:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num21:8-Num21:9\">NUM 21:8–21:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh3:13-Josh3:17\">JOS 3:13–3:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs17:5\">1KI 17:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs4:41\">2KI 4:41</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs5:10-2Kgs5:14\">2KI 5:10–5:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt9:6-Matt9:7\">MAT 9:6–9:7</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark2:10-Mark2:12\">MRK 2:10–2:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke5:24-Luke5:25\">LUK 5:24–5:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt9:22\">MAT 9:22</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark5:34\">MRK 5:34</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke8:48\">LUK 8:48</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke1:38\">LUK 1:38</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb11:29-Heb11:30\">HEB 11:29–11:30</a></p>\n<h2>Miracles limited by lack of faith</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt13:58\">MAT 13:58</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark6:5-Mark6:6\">MRK 6:5–6:6</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs4:3-2Kgs4:6\">2KI 4:3–4:6</a> <em>The number of jars limited the miraculous supply of oil</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt14:28-Matt14:31\">MAT 14:28–14:31</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt17:14-Matt17:20\">MAT 17:14–17:20</a></p>\n<h2>Positive responses to miracles</h2>\n<h3>Faith</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod14:31\">EXO 14:31</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod4:30-Exod4:31\">EXO 4:30–4:31</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John7:31\">JHN 7:31</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts9:33-Acts9:35\">ACT 9:33–9:35</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts9:40-Acts9:42\">ACT 9:40–9:42</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts13:12\">ACT 13:12</a></p>\n<h3>Amazement</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt15:31\">MAT 15:31</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark7:37\">MRK 7:37</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan3:24\">DAN 3:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts3:10\">ACT 3:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts8:13\">ACT 8:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts12:16\">ACT 12:16</a></p>\n<h3>Praise and worship</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts3:8\">ACT 3:8</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod15:11\">EXO 15:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod15:21\">EXO 15:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps9:1\">PSA 9:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan3:28\">DAN 3:28</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan4:2-Dan4:3\">DAN 4:2–4:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan6:26-Dan6:27\">DAN 6:26–6:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt15:31\">MAT 15:31</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke19:37\">LUK 19:37</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts4:21-Acts4:22\">ACT 4:21–4:22</a></p>\n<h3>A closer attention paid to the word of God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts8:6\">ACT 8:6</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs17:24\">1KI 17:24</a></p>\n<h2>Temporary faith as a response to miracles</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John2:23-John2:24\">JHN 2:23–2:24</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod15:20-Exod15:24\">EXO 15:20–15:24</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod16:1-Exod16:3\">EXO 16:1–16:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod17:3\">EXO 17:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num20:3-Num20:5\">NUM 20:3–20:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke17:17-Luke17:18\">LUK 17:17–17:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John6:49\">JHN 6:49</a></p>\n<h2>Negative responses to miracles</h2>\n<h3>Fear</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark5:15-Mark5:17\">MRK 5:15–5:17</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke8:36-Luke8:37\">LUK 8:36–8:37</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts5:5\">ACT 5:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts5:11\">ACT 5:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts19:17\">ACT 19:17</a></p>\n<h3>Disbelief</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts12:14-Acts12:15\">ACT 12:14–12:15</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen17:17-Gen17:18\">GEN 17:17–17:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen18:12-Gen18:13\">GEN 18:12–18:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke1:18\">LUK 1:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke1:20\">LUK 1:20</a></p>\n<h3>Hardness of heart</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod8:19\">EXO 8:19</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod7:3-Exod7:4\">EXO 7:3–7:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod11:10\">EXO 11:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps78:32\">PSA 78:32</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt11:20-Matt11:22\">MAT 11:20–11:22</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke10:13-Luke10:14\">LUK 10:13–10:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John9:18\">JHN 9:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John9:28-John9:29\">JHN 9:28–9:29</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John10:25-John10:26\">JHN 10:25–10:26</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John12:37\">JHN 12:37</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John15:24\">JHN 15:24</a></p>\n<h3>Opposition</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John11:47-John11:48\">JHN 11:47–11:48</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts6:8-Acts6:9\">ACT 6:8–6:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts16:19-Acts16:21\">ACT 16:19–16:21</a></p>\n<h3>Disobedience</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps106:7\">PSA 106:7</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num14:11\">NUM 14:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num14:22-Num14:23\">NUM 14:22–14:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps78:11-Ps78:22\">PSA 78:11–78:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps78:42-Ps78:43\">PSA 78:42–78:43</a></p>\n<h3>Jealousy</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts8:13\">ACT 8:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts8:18-Acts8:19\">ACT 8:18–8:19</a></p>",
